  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ATTACK OF THE JERSEY DRONES</strong> is a short and simple Virtual Reality game about FREEDOM and PRIVACY!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3491650/extras/51458542147ac7e9cb36434b57171d38.poster.avif?t=1747956295\" width=434 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3491650/extras/51458542147ac7e9cb36434b57171d38.webm?t=1747956295\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3491650/extras/51458542147ac7e9cb36434b57171d38.mp4?t=1747956295\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a retired war veteran, all you wanted was to live the rest of your days out in peace and quiet. <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3491650/extras/d17a56917d6e22f2a2a8670e406360da.poster.avif?t=1747956295\" width=434 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3491650/extras/d17a56917d6e22f2a2a8670e406360da.webm?t=1747956295\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3491650/extras/d17a56917d6e22f2a2a8670e406360da.mp4?t=1747956295\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unfortunately for you, a swarm of drones (WHO COULD THEY POSSIBLY BE?) won't leave you alone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3491650/extras/07927b8c67217e3562d6063f4f2601e7.poster.avif?t=1747956295\" width=434 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3491650/extras/07927b8c67217e3562d6063f4f2601e7.webm?t=1747956295\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3491650/extras/07927b8c67217e3562d6063f4f2601e7.mp4?t=1747956295\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So there's only one thing to do. DEFEND. YOUR. FREEDOM!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3491650/extras/fc6563369035da04243f4e97cf70b4af.poster.avif?t=1747956295\" width=434 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3491650/extras/fc6563369035da04243f4e97cf70b4af.webm?t=1747956295\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3491650/extras/fc6563369035da04243f4e97cf70b4af.mp4?t=1747956295\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Overview</strong>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 15-30 minutes of Pure Patriotism! <br>- Shoot down an aggressive hoard of drones invading your neighborhood<br>- Unlock various classic American firearms (M1911, M16A1, UZI, M134 Minigun)<br>- Intuitive, easy-to-understand gameplay  <br>- Roomscale experience. No need to worry about motion sickness!</p>",
